{"tid":211510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"都四年啦…以為自己已經放低左","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T13:51:12.000Z","uid":98645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68478b6cc5cb1251e973152cfff1a0d0eee94941","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"唉屌 我係咪無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打屌醒我又好 有人有共鳴又好<br />\n搵人同我講吓野 好撚灰鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉我知好撚長氣 但無計<br />\n因為成件事都發生都幾耐<br />\n<br />\n女神係中學識 識就唔只四年<br />\n仲有聯絡 到而家都幾friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有幾close過 唔算係毒撚高攀嗰種 <br />\n有段時間真係好鍾意佢 <br />\n差啲儲夠氣直接表白<br />\n本身有時都會單獨出街玩 食飯睇戲<br />\n但自己慢熱型 等等吓錯過晒時機 <br />\n莫講話要表白完仲要一齊到 <br />\n後來去到係講嘅機會都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為四年前有次兩個去玩完食野<br />\n佢無端端同我講要去同另一個男仔表白<br />\n我已經估到係邊個 直接問左係咪佢<br />\n女神仲話我乜咁勁咁都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成餐飯唔知自己答左乜 印象中仲叫佢加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過幾日佢好開心黎話我知佢地一齊<br />\n就同嗰條仔拍拖到而家<br />\n<br />\n其實本身都淡左好多 <br />\n因為知佢之前幾任都好撚仆街或者奇怪<br />\n但同而家呢個佢好幸福 而就算有乜都輪唔到我<br />\n但佢仲係對我好好 又好好傾<br />\n啱啱要約common friend嘅聚會打去搵佢<br />\n佢其實啱啱旅完行番黎無耐<br />\n傾完要約去邊有無preference食乜之後<br />\n我話交比我搞叫佢休息吓<br />\n臨收線無端端叫住我 話<br />\n「你啊，記得睇吓信箱有無收到我postcard」 <br />\n屌 但係個地址已經係好耐之前比佢<br />\n肯寫postcard其一 有keep住我地址其二<br />\n聽到嗰吓都依然係好心動<br />\n唔係要同佢一齊嗰種心情 <br />\n但原來佢喺我心入面點都係有個重要嘅位置<br />\n<br />\n無喇無喇 咁可能就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e504f89cfe0b34ce19b571e2d631fa717d546d2c","tid":211510,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"佢記憶力好姐 個個人地址都記得"},{"pid":"0884274753f72e8a7755aafe06edd56f8f1b15d2","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢記憶力好姐 個個人地址都記得</blockquote><br />\n佢好懶 無心寫一定唔會肯寫<br />\n就算當係派軍糧都好 起碼我係有include喺入面"},{"pid":"a794e0e17e4ed65bfda32047894318451f02ea38","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢記憶力好姐 個個人地址都記得</blockquote><br />\n佢好懶 無心寫一定唔會肯寫<br />\n就算當係派軍糧都好 起碼我係有include喺入面</blockquote><br />\n我係咪好cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab54c9e7c810e0c73ea3abc4be682dc2045012d0","tid":211510,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢記憶力好姐 個個人地址都記得</blockquote><br />\n佢好懶 無心寫一定唔會肯寫<br />\n就算當係派軍糧都好 起碼我係有include喺入面</blockquote><br />\n我係咪好cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢同個男仔表白之後點"},{"pid":"914343d95c016181c2489736f56a0f0d9b9dcec7","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"個感覺係比起我初戀更加初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想之後成日有個陰影/比較 求屌醒"},{"pid":"29281bc62a53e32759a715120382ac8fb62a01c6","tid":211510,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個感覺係比起我初戀更加初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想之後成日有個陰影/比較 求屌醒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c43a6b8870cf6001298a8ad80de8f233f01d99","tid":211510,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"用人地條女黎有初戀feel"},{"pid":"697bbbc68720b555cc5d8ffa58bca2f7768b3953","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢記憶力好姐 個個人地址都記得</blockquote><br />\n佢好懶 無心寫一定唔會肯寫<br />\n就算當係派軍糧都好 起碼我係有include喺入面</blockquote><br />\n我係咪好cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢同個男仔表白之後點</blockquote><br />\n個男仔無即刻應承 但過幾日都一齊左<br />\n一路到而家都係同一條仔 好穩定"},{"pid":"298561d1a8bd04116199c1adf7720f77746aa3fd","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用人地條女黎有初戀feel</blockquote><br />\n係囉 屌 明明甚至都無一齊過"},{"pid":"6479fb1313dc842a0898a88fdee1bf3c00012e84","tid":211510,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"正 一張postcard 就派到兵糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f66f200bd1b439d04778544a803f3a93151f160","tid":211510,"uid":59569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"靠意志力"},{"pid":"f21832bd824d91e6b4bc5724cf98f3a5eff3a8c4","tid":211510,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用人地條女黎有初戀feel</blockquote><br />\n係囉 屌 明明甚至都無一齊過</blockquote><br />\n就好似條女同條扑野 你係隔離打飛機咁"},{"pid":"f237a39386c07213fdaea26a61d0adab1db5b97a","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正 一張postcard 就派到兵糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁今時今日用手寫字 有實體有張紙嘅野比較少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係好撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22706a50d8d26251213e4da015ae37b68fbb7f03","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用人地條女黎有初戀feel</blockquote><br />\n係囉 屌 明明甚至都無一齊過</blockquote><br />\n就好似條女同條扑野 你係隔離打飛機咁</blockquote><br />\n係囉 好撚柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果我每次都可以咁理智咁判斷就好"},{"pid":"306f460b0335d06d547186e0ac3c3741b95082f3","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"道理其實都明 但係心動呢啲無得控制<br />\n覺得自己好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"951fd478042633de076e11f53b07d9086d80a8ad","tid":211510,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"手寫既野真係好感動...望住佢字跡就覺得好似望到佢寫字個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85d6e2e06d73497decf9ec886a46ede77525b25","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手寫既野真係好感動...望住佢字跡就覺得好似望到佢寫字個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆 就算係朋友寫比自己都warm 何況係鍾意過嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5219a11d76778a4a5f85a991edf73a3dc50064bb","tid":211510,"uid":81383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"你快d搵過條女 有d寄託好無"},{"pid":"daa2f39521c708c20d2801af977642756143a150","tid":211510,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"比男朋友更close既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5b8e7a3239392332d661077c524377dd955eec","tid":211510,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"巴打我雖然冇你咁耐,<br />\n過左2年都以為自己已經放低左<br />\n不過自己感覺係冇得呃"},{"pid":"eb3abc6d462d5f4c84dbad1f5070bd62aca01bec","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你快d搵過條女 有d寄託好無</blockquote><br />\n但如果咁係咪對條女有啲唔公平 好似利用人黎比自己有寄託 一個收兵嘅循環"},{"pid":"624c36216ac3e7b541ea5bd5e9f85cadb95a91ab","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比男朋友更close既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知佢知唔知我鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果知左係咪尷尬到唔會再聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c8d6cba7af75264109e49efe9e198772fb9ee5","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我雖然冇你咁耐,<br />\n過左2年都以為自己已經放低左<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">自己感覺係冇得呃</span></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想叫自己收皮 <br />\nbtw 巴打要唔要分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263094d6323b51d3d08c5a7dd673cd083173fc0b","tid":211510,"uid":104260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正 一張postcard 就派到兵糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁今時今日用手寫字 有實體有張紙嘅野比較少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係好撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真 個人係咪中意自己 <br />\n女仔係一定知 你仲做到出撚哂面<br />\n一個好女仔無論有無男朋友<br />\n如果佢覺得同你無可能<br />\n一定會主動遠離你 等你唔好咁多幻想<br />\n依家佢有男朋友<br />\n都唔識同中意自己既男仔保持距離<br />\n連登仔實話依挺正臭閪<br />\n<br />\n你好好衡量下咁既女仔值唔值得你放咁多心機同時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得每個人都有被愛既資格同機會<br />\n你唔離開佢 就等如你親手放棄依個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c897e05493ac2bedcbf7cd0d095f72d8e2c5a9b","tid":211510,"uid":92236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"冷靜期緊每分每秒都諗住佢 放唔低 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7cf1d293b86bfdfa2a9d2e1c2db8b4c557a061","tid":211510,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:42